1180
00:51:14,620 --> 00:51:16,000
 I Bog nju počinje

1181
00:51:16,000 --> 00:51:17,040
 dijelom i sam voditi.

1182
00:51:17,040 --> 00:51:17,880
 Više nije tu samo

1183
00:51:17,880 --> 00:51:19,500
