1184
00:51:19,500 --> 00:51:20,820
 nego Bog počinje

1185
00:51:20,820 --> 00:51:22,500
 sam voditi tu osobu također.

1186
00:51:22,980 --> 00:51:24,420
 Sveti Bernard u ovoj fazi

1187
00:51:24,420 --> 00:51:25,560
 kaže sloboda duha.

1188
00:51:25,560 --> 00:51:27,740
 Ljubiti druge kao sebe samog

1189
00:51:27,740 --> 00:51:29,160
 nadaje ući se dobitku

1190
00:51:29,160 --> 00:51:29,940
 njihove ljubavi.

1191
00:51:29,940 --> 00:51:30,900
 Znači, to još uvijek

1192
00:51:30,900 --> 00:51:31,940
 nije savršena ljubav,

1193
00:51:31,940 --> 00:51:33,020
 ali mi počinjemo

1194
00:51:33,020 --> 00:51:34,040
 ljubiti druge

1195
00:51:34,040 --> 00:51:35,620
 zbog ljubavi

1196
00:51:35,620 --> 00:51:37,060
 koju dobijamo za uzvrat.

1197
00:51:37,060 --> 00:51:37,980
 Znači, to još uvijek

1198
00:51:37,980 --> 00:51:39,920
 nije ona savršena ljubav.

1199
00:51:39,920 --> 00:51:41,700
 Ljubljenje Kristovih ruku,

1200
00:51:41,700 --> 00:51:43,060
 to znači krepost,

1201
00:51:43,060 --> 00:51:44,060
 molitva, plodovi,

1202
00:51:44,060 --> 00:51:45,340
