1213
00:51:59,340 --> 00:52:03,340
 I sam sam bio u toj fazi,

1214
00:52:03,340 --> 00:52:04,800
 pa i sad sam.

1215
00:52:04,800 --> 00:52:08,140
 Kaže dalje,

1216
00:52:08,140 --> 00:52:11,260
 rastu krepostima.

1217
00:52:11,260 --> 00:52:13,280
 Znači, Sveti Franjo-Saleški

1218
00:52:13,280 --> 00:52:14,660
 kaže za fazu prosvjetljenja

1219
00:52:14,660 --> 00:52:15,660
 rastu krepostima

1220
00:52:15,660 --> 00:52:16,980
 poniznosti, poslušnosti,

1221
00:52:16,980 --> 00:52:17,640
 strpljivosti,

1222
00:52:17,640 --> 00:52:18,540
 siromašu duha,

1223
00:52:18,540 --> 00:52:19,560
 nenavezanosti,

1224
00:52:19,560 --> 00:52:21,020
 postojanosti u molitvi

1225
00:52:21,020 --> 00:52:22,220
 i ljubavi prabližnjima,

1226
00:52:22,220 --> 00:52:23,560
 plaćenička ljubav,

1227
00:52:23,560 --> 00:52:24,980
 sluga koji traži plaću.

1228
00:52:24,980 --> 00:52:25,860
 Još uvijek se traži

1229
00:52:25,860 --> 00:52:27,180
 šta ja dobijam za uzvrat.

1230
00:52:27,180 --> 00:52:28,360
 Bilo od ljudi,

1231
00:52:28,360 --> 00:52:29,320
 bilo od Boga.

1232
00:52:29,320 --> 00:52:30,920
 Međutim, sve jasnije

1233
00:52:30,920 --> 00:52:32,200
 imamo u vidu duhovni svijet

1234
00:52:32,200 --> 00:52:33,260
 i postojamo pomalo

1235
00:52:33,260 --> 00:52:34,640
 Boži prijatelji.

1236
00:52:34,640 --> 00:52:36,100
 I zadnji,

1237
00:52:36,100 --> 00:52:37,040
