1249
00:52:51,660 --> 00:52:53,380
 nego Bog radi kroz vas.

1250
00:52:53,380 --> 00:52:55,120
 Vaše cijelo biće

1251
00:52:55,120 --> 00:52:55,920
 je predano Bogu

1252
00:52:55,920 --> 00:52:56,720
 i Bog se služi

1253
00:52:56,720 --> 00:52:57,840
 svakom vašom riječju,

1254
00:52:57,840 --> 00:52:59,400
 svakim vašim pogledom.

1255
00:52:59,400 --> 00:53:00,400
 Često u slučaju

1256
00:53:00,400 --> 00:53:01,120
