1263
00:53:09,360 --> 00:53:10,940
 Joj, kako ću sad postiti.

1264
00:53:10,940 --> 00:53:11,580
 Ne.

1265
00:53:11,580 --> 00:53:12,320
 Zato se čini

1266
00:53:12,320 --> 00:53:13,640
