1267
00:53:13,640 --> 00:53:14,920
 A ljudi zaboravaju

1268
00:53:14,920 --> 00:53:16,880
 ovo što je do toga dovelo.

1269
00:53:16,880 --> 00:53:18,200
 Vidjeti čovjeka

1270
00:53:18,200 --> 00:53:18,860
 koji u ovoj fazi

1271
00:53:18,860 --> 00:53:19,580
 imao sam priliku

1272
00:53:19,580 --> 00:53:20,520
 nekoliko ljudi

1273
00:53:20,520 --> 00:53:21,560
 takvih vidjeti

1274
00:53:21,560 --> 00:53:22,100
 jednostavno.

1275
00:53:22,100 --> 00:53:22,980
 Kao da gledate

1276
00:53:22,980 --> 00:53:23,660
 raj na zemlji.

1277
00:53:23,660 --> 00:53:24,840
 Oni su komadić neba

1278
00:53:24,840 --> 00:53:25,280
 na zemlji.

1279
00:53:25,280 --> 00:53:26,460
 Oni su po sve prožiti

1280
00:53:26,460 --> 00:53:26,840
 Bogom.

1281
00:53:26,840 --> 00:53:27,860
 I normalni su.

1282
00:53:29,860 --> 00:53:34,580
 Neki od njih su

1283
00:53:34,580 --> 00:53:35,560
