1284
00:53:35,560 --> 00:53:41,060
 Na, normalni su.

1285
00:53:41,060 --> 00:53:42,400
 Idu na WC,

1286
00:53:42,400 --> 00:53:43,140
 vode ljubav

1287
00:53:43,140 --> 00:53:44,240
 sa mužem i ženom,

1288
00:53:44,240 --> 00:53:45,680
 odgajaju djecu

1289
00:53:45,680 --> 00:53:46,860
 i dalje idu na posao.

1290
00:53:46,860 --> 00:53:48,740
 Sve normalno.

1291
00:53:48,740 --> 00:53:50,720
 Samo što su radosti.

1292
00:53:50,720 --> 00:53:51,740
 Samo što su slobodni.

1293
00:53:51,740 --> 00:53:53,300
 Samo što su ispunjeni.

1294
00:53:53,300 --> 00:53:56,380
 Svet Ivan od Križa

1295
00:53:56,380 --> 00:53:56,640
 kaže

1296
00:53:56,640 --> 00:53:57,380
 savršeno,

1297
00:53:57,380 --> 00:53:57,860
 trajno,

1298
00:53:57,860 --> 00:53:58,740
 kontemplativno

1299
00:53:58,740 --> 00:53:59,280
 sjedinjenje,

1300
00:53:59,280 --> 00:54:00,300
 duhovna ženitba,

1301
00:54:00,300 --> 00:54:01,480
 preobražavanje,

1302
00:54:01,480 --> 00:54:02,920
 preobražavajuće

1303
00:54:02,920 --> 00:54:03,680
 sjedinjenje.

1304
00:54:03,680 --> 00:54:04,500
 Znači,

1305
00:54:04,500 --> 00:54:05,920
 to kao što se u spolnom činu

1306
00:54:05,920 --> 00:54:06,880
 događa potpuno

1307
00:54:06,880 --> 00:54:07,480
 sjedinjenje

1308
00:54:07,480 --> 00:54:08,500
 bračnih partnera,

1309
00:54:08,500 --> 00:54:09,460
 tako ovdje,

1310
00:54:09,460 --> 00:54:10,740
 ako gledamo o crkvu

1311
00:54:10,740 --> 00:54:11,720
 kao zaručnicu,

1312
00:54:11,720 --> 00:54:12,280
 se događa

1313
00:54:12,280 --> 00:54:13,240
 sjedinjenje duše

1314
00:54:13,240 --> 00:54:13,740
 s Bogom.

1315
00:54:13,740 --> 00:54:14,940
 Duše je potpuno

1316
00:54:14,940 --> 00:54:15,440
 ispunjena

1317
00:54:15,440 --> 00:54:16,120
 i tu dolazimo

1318
00:54:16,120 --> 00:54:17,080
 do onog ispunjenja

1319
00:54:17,080 --> 00:54:18,120
 svake želje.

1320
00:54:18,120 --> 00:54:19,160
 Vjerujte mi,

1321
00:54:19,160 --> 00:54:20,160
