1329
00:54:33,860 --> 00:54:35,200
 I mi nosimo u sebi

1330
00:54:35,200 --> 00:54:36,200
 sjećanje na Eden

1331
00:54:36,200 --> 00:54:37,260
 i čežnju

1332
00:54:37,260 --> 00:54:38,440
 za Bogom.

1333
00:54:38,440 --> 00:54:39,460
 Samo što nam je Bog

1334
00:54:39,460 --> 00:54:40,920
 često bio krivo predstavljen.

1335
00:54:40,920 --> 00:54:42,240
 Samo što smo

1336
00:54:42,240 --> 00:54:43,260
